### Logout User
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: auth_token={{authToken}}

### Verify Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify
Cookie: auth_token={{authToken}}

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Cookie: auth_token={{authToken}}

### Alternative way to authenticate using Authorization header
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

